WEBVTT


00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:03.160
how do you know if you were in a toxic romantic relationship

00:00:03.161 --> 00:00:06.340
well one of the ways I found in run like Hell

00:00:06.480 --> 00:00:09.580
Nadine Macaluso new book about trauma bonds

00:00:09.640 --> 00:00:12.040
is going through the Pathological Lover Checklist

00:00:12.041 --> 00:00:14.860
which kind of helps gear you to sort of

00:00:14.880 --> 00:00:17.520
take an inventory of the behaviours of your romantic partner

00:00:17.521 --> 00:00:19.880
and see whether they are toxic

00:00:19.881 --> 00:00:23.120
or have some sort of pathological underlying reasons

00:00:23.121 --> 00:00:24.200
so here's the checklist

00:00:24.201 --> 00:00:26.740
how much of your partner do you see in the following behaviours

00:00:27.040 --> 00:00:29.800
speaks disrespectfully about his former partners

00:00:29.801 --> 00:00:34.520
is deceitful and you catch him in lies is disrespectful towards

00:00:34.521 --> 00:00:37.160
belittles or insults you is dominating

00:00:37.161 --> 00:00:40.220
wants to control your behavior and restrict whom you connect with

00:00:40.400 --> 00:00:45.840
blames you for everything is possessive and unnecessarily jealous lacks remorse

00:00:45.841 --> 00:00:49.180
guilt or compassion is intimidating or threatening

00:00:49.240 --> 00:00:51.700
is superficially charming in public

00:00:51.800 --> 00:00:52.720
and those are just a few

00:00:52.721 --> 00:00:55.080
there's several more that you wanna check out in her new book

00:00:55.081 --> 00:00:56.500
you can find it on TikTok Shop
